        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR2a0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:26:09.072+09:00">Master Sun Wu</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:26:20.724+09:00">was a person from Qi.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:26:42.149+09:00">Due to [his] military method [he] was granted an audience by the king of Wu, Helu.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:26:51.838+09:00">Helu said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:27:10.895+09:00">"Your thirteen chapters</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:27:19.81+09:00">I have examined entirely.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:27:32.202+09:00">Is a little test of drilling troops possible?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:27:41.518+09:00">[Master Sun] answered:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:28:04.034+09:00">"[It is] possible."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:28:13.285+09:00">Helu said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:28:24.523+09:00">"Is it possible to test with women?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:28:37.757+09:00">[Master Sun] said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:28:46.241+09:00">"It is possible."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:29:19.846+09:00">Whereupon [the king] permitted him</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:29:36.717+09:00">to bring out from the palace beautiful maidens</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:29:52.204+09:00">[and] get a hundred and eighty of them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:30:10.024+09:00">Master Sun divided [them] into two units</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:30:29.888+09:00">and made each of the king’s two favourite concubines a unit leader.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:30:57.823+09:00">To all [of them he] commanded to hold halberds,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:31:12.358+09:00">[then] said commandingly:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:31:36.426+09:00">"Do you know [where are] your heart, left and right hands, and back?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:31:49.836+09:00">The women said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:33:17.395+09:00">"We do."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:33:36.973+09:00">Master Sun said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:33:57.149+09:00">"[On the command] 'ahead',</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:34:12.904+09:00">then look in [the direction of your] heart;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:34:32.77+09:00">'left', look at [your] left-hand [side],</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:34:56.54+09:00">[and] 'right', at [your] right-hand [side];</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:35:32.154+09:00">'rear', then look back."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:35:44.459+09:00">The women said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:35:54.299+09:00">"Agreed."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:36:17.648+09:00">The stipulations being stated,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:36:30.838+09:00">[the executioner’s] axe was laid out,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:36:40.893+09:00">then the three commands were repeated five times.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:37:02.195+09:00">Whereupon [the command] "right" was drummed.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:37:14.056+09:00">The women laughed greatly.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:37:21.526+09:00">Master Sun said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:37:37.813+09:00">"[When] the stipulations are not clear</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:37:55.647+09:00">[and] repeated commands not familiar [to the troops],</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:38:07.501+09:00">the commander is to blame."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:38:31.897+09:00">Again [he] repeated five times the three commands, and [the command] "left" was drummed.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:38:44.288+09:00">The women laughed greatly again.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:38:48.425+09:00">Master Sun said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:39:10.512+09:00">"[When] the stipulations are not clear</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:39:24.024+09:00">[and] repeated commands not familiar [to the troops],</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:39:33.628+09:00">the commander is to blame;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:39:54.415+09:00">in case [these] have been clarified, but the method is not followed,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:40:07.643+09:00">the officers are to blame."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:41:31.512+09:00">Thus [he] prepared (or: wanted) [to have] the left and right unit leaders executed.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:41:39.672+09:00">The king of Wu, who was observing from atop a terrace,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:41:48.184+09:00">saw [his] beloved concubines about to be executed</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:41:59.162+09:00">[and] was greatly startled.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:42:08.666+09:00">In haste [he] sent down a messenger to command:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:42:24.252+09:00">"General, we already know [your] capability to use troops.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.56" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:43:15.451+09:00">Without these two concubines,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.57" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:43:08.365+09:00">our food would be tasteless.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:43:36.234+09:00">[We] wish that [they] not be executed."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:43:48.984+09:00">Master Sun said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:43:56.308+09:00">"[Your] servant has already accepted [your] order to act as commander.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:44:03.758+09:00">[When] the commander is with the army,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.62" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:44:15.506+09:00">there are orders from the sovereign that [he] does not obey."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.63" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:44:26.209+09:00">[He] forthwith [had] the two unit leaders executed to set an example,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.64" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:44:34.179+09:00">and used their next in line as unit leaders.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.65" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:44:41.571+09:00">Whereupon [he] drummed again.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.66" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:44:54.364+09:00">The women [looked] right and left, ahead and to the rear, knelt and stood up, all squarely matching the prescribed rules,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.67" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:45:01.234+09:00">without daring to emit a sound.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.68" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:45:09.402+09:00">Whereupon Master Sun sent a messenger to report to the king:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.69" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:45:17.792+09:00">"The troops have been arranged in formation,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.70" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:45:26.507+09:00">the king may try coming down to inspect them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.71" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:45:34.289+09:00">Let the king use them in whatever intent,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.72" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:45:42.783+09:00">even throwing [them] into water or fire is equally possible."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.73" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:45:51.81+09:00">The king of Wu said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.74" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:46:04.691+09:00">"[Let] the general abandon [the drill] and retire to [his] quarters.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.75" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:46:12.914+09:00">We wish not to come down for an inspection."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.76" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:46:21.893+09:00">Master Sun said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.77" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:46:49.662+09:00">"The king is merely fond of his words,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.78" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:46:47.2+09:00">[he] is incapable of putting them into practice."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.79" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:47:02.475+09:00">Whereupon Helu knew Master Sun’s capability to use troops,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.80" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:47:15.512+09:00">[and] eventually made him commander.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.81" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:47:23.774+09:00">To the West, [Wu] crushed the powerful [state of] Chu</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.82" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-05T23:38:02.25+09:00">and entered Ying.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.83" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:47:53.719+09:00">To the North, [Wu] overawed [the states of] Qi and Jin.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.84" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:48:09.423+09:00">[Helu’s] name [became] illustrious [among] the feudatories,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_065-1a.85" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-04T02:48:22.656+09:00">[and] Master Sun contributed strongly [to it].</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
